(3) Reports. Submittal to congress . Not later than one year after the date of the enactment of this Act, the Secretary of Defense shall submit to the congressional defense committees a report that includes - (A) the plan developed under paragraph (1); and 
(B) with respect to each recommendation described in paragraph (2)(B) that the Secretary has implemented or expects to implement - (i) Summary. a summary of actions that have been taken to implement the recommendation; and 
(ii) Schedule. a schedule, with specific milestones, for completing the implementation of the recommendation. 



